{"id":42,"parent_id":0,"book_id":80,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":42,"title":"Chapter 39: Nephi Receives Great Power","subtitle":"","short_title":"Chapter 39","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"chapter","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.head1"},[".titleNumber","Chapter 39"],["h1","Nephi Receives Great Power"]],[".bodyBlock",[".image",{"id":"f1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.f1"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_042_01.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p3"},"Nephi walked toward his home, thinking about what the Lord had shown him and about the wickedness of the Nephites. He was sad because of their wickedness."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p4"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/10.1-3"},"Helaman 10:1–3"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f2","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.f2"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_042_02.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p5"},"The Lord spoke to Nephi and praised him for being obedient and working so hard to teach the gospel."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p6"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/10.4"},"Helaman 10:4"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.f3"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_042_03.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p7"},"Nephi was given the power to do anything. The Lord knew he would use this power righteously."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p8"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/10.5"},"Helaman 10:5"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.f4"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_042_04.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p9"},"The Lord told Nephi to warn the Nephites that if they did not repent, they would be destroyed. Nephi went immediately to warn the people."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p10"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/10.11-12"},"Helaman 10:11–12"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.f5"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_042_05.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p11"},"The Nephites did not believe Nephi. They tried to throw him into prison, but the power of God protected him."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p12"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/10.15-16"},"Helaman 10:15–16"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.f6"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_042_06.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p13"},"Nephi declared the word of God to all the Nephites."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p14"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/10.17"},"Helaman 10:17"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.f7"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_042_07.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p15"},"But the people became even more wicked and began fighting each other."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p16"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/11.1"},"Helaman 11:1"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.f8"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_042_08.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p17"},"Nephi prayed for a famine, hoping that a lack of food would humble the Nephites and help them repent."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p18","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p18"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/11.3-4"},"Helaman 11:3–4"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.f9"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_042_09.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p19","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p19"},"The famine came. There was no rain, so the ground dried up and crops could not grow. The people stopped fighting."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p20","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p20"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/11.5-6"},"Helaman 11:5–6"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.f10"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_042_10.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p21","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p21"},"The Nephites were hungry, and many of them died. Those who lived began to remember the Lord and what Nephi had taught them."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p22","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p22"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/11.6-7"},"Helaman 11:6–7"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.f11"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_042_11.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p23","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p23"},"The people repented of their sins and then begged their judges to ask Nephi to end the famine. The judges went to Nephi."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p24","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p24"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/11.8-9"},"Helaman 11:8–9"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.f12"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_042_12.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p25","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p25"},"When Nephi saw that the people had become humble and had repented, he asked the Lord to end the famine."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p26","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p26"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/11.9-12"},"Helaman 11:9–12"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.f13"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_042_13.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p27","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p27"},"The Lord answered Nephi’s prayer, and it began to rain. Soon the crops were growing again. The people glorified God and knew that Nephi was a great prophet."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p28","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p28"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/11.17-18"},"Helaman 11:17–18"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.f14"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_042_14.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p29","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p29"},"Most of the Nephites joined the Church. They became rich, and their cities grew. There was peace in the land."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p30","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p30"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/11.20-21"},"Helaman 11:20–21"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.f15"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_042_15.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p31","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p31"},"Then some Nephites who had earlier joined the Lamanites attacked the Nephites."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p32","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p32"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/11.24"},"Helaman 11:24"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.f16"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_042_16.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p33","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p33"},"The Nephites tried to defeat their enemies, who had become Gadianton robbers, but could not because they themselves had become wicked again."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p34","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p34"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/11.26,28-29"},"Helaman 11:26, 28–29"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.f17"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_042_17.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p35","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p35"},"When the Nephites were righteous, the Lord blessed them. When they were proud and forgot the Lord, he gave them problems to help them remember him."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p36","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-39-nephi-receives-great-power.p36"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.1-3"},"Helaman 12:1–3"]]]]]]]],"refs":null}
